    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like such a waste. like i'm sitting here trying to build this life, and work, and relationships... but in a few billion years the sun is just gonna swallow everything anyway. the heat death is inevitable. nothing we do actually sticks. what's even the point of struggling through the day when the end result is just absolute nothingness?",
